{"tid":1476163,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"如果叫連仔開多幾個台會唔會太過份？","createTime":"2019-08-15T17:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T14:25:38.000Z","uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3be4273353aaa769ceedfd9ba4a33930286c0be7","tid":1476163,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:17:34.000Z","msg":"借fd ac一用<br />\n初次出po好多唔識如有不足請大家幫忙指出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講明先：對管理/設立討論區呢方面0認識，只係想提出意見睇下有冇機會做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為呢場運動，上連登已經成為左好多人嘅生活習慣。大家都喺度宣傳討論交流，日日都有成千上萬個po<br />\n亦因此出現左啲問題：<br />\n1.好多人出po令到各位出嘅po好快就俾人沉底(sorry唔係好識講<br />\n2.日日太多資訊都冇耐性睇曬咁多，可能就咁miss左啲重要野/好快唔記得(香港人出名善忘🤦🏻&zwj;♀️)<br />\n3.巴打絲打們重複po文宣圖睇到都辛苦<br />\n4.作為用家有時睇到排山倒海嘅po都好攰，會特登唔上連登等自己冷靜下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以如果請連仔開多幾個台有冇可能？作分流之用。<br />\n例如：文宣台，意見台，戰略台，活動台，同呢場運動相關嘅消息台等等(呢啲名都係隨意諗，如果可行再改<br />\n<br />\n或者會令到啲po觸及率低左但係會方便返用戶搵返各自需要嘅資料，各位做野都會更加有效率。<br />\n<br />\n以上係本人嘅拙見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但希望可以解決到呢個pain point"},{"pid":"0f90e76bc880947ef488490c22faae04432637e0","tid":1476163,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:31:19.000Z","msg":"另外都想增加留名上限"},{"pid":"61acb50a34b75d00c2e4ed04eab9554064124a31","tid":1476163,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:31:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a00d8177433bedf8948656057c9aebc201ab59ce","tid":1476163,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:31:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"733ac7762080bfe7797e26bee0b4d2d7444cdaa5","tid":1476163,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:32:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17baf5116cc8cbdf6b0d8d76abd451e3f96018f5","tid":1476163,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:32:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36c0bbff6c3c0294e42db50a124f057369013c37","tid":1476163,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:32:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a7da03e0f4f143eea0f851fd1b51ad9dc8392f5","tid":1476163,"uid":267763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:33:06.000Z","msg":"連仔睇到嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a04e420c1b4909d776c9c9a6b6631da4d27d7b","tid":1476163,"uid":223664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}